a252beda-7e0b-4dc7-afd5-29c4a4c59340.title: FIFA 25
a252beda-7e0b-4dc7-afd5-29c4a4c59340.summary: Buoyed by a new strategy engine (FC IQ) an emphasis on 5-on-5 (Rush), and women's modes, FC 25 is a nice upgrade from FC 24. If Pro Evolution Soccer and Football Manager had a next gen console lovechild, it would likely appear as FC 25.

c9ef5e86-4936-4ebe-97ce-3051c77a8e76.title: Grand Theft Auto V
c9ef5e86-4936-4ebe-97ce-3051c77a8e76.summary: Grand Theft Auto V is an action-adventure game played from either a third-person or first-person perspective. Players complete missions—linear scenarios with set objectives—to progress through the story. Outside of the missions, players may freely roam the open world.

cd649293-3593-4458-882f-cce83de8ba9c.title: Need for Speed
cd649293-3593-4458-882f-cce83de8ba9c.summary: Need for Speed (NFS) is a racing game franchise published by Electronic Arts. The series centers around illegal street racing and tasks players to complete various types of races while evading the local law enforcement in police pursuits. The original game, The Need for Speed, was released in 1994 and has been ported to various platforms.
